snippet.title: Johnny Depp Happly Reacts To Amber Heard Losing in Court Again!
snippet.description:
💙Johnny Depp Happly Reacts To Amber Heard Losing in Court Again!
Johnny Depp is currently pursuing a $50 million defamation trial against Amber Heard, alleging that various allegations of abuse are not true. Depp's team bluntly stated that the photo of two bruises under Heard's eyes was fake. And because it was being used in an ongoing lawsuit, Depp was able to request access to Herd's phone.
